    "created_at": "2015-06-11T19:19:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-06-11T19:19:13Z",
    "body": "This is definitely not the best approach.\n\nInhibiting the screensaver is a platform-specific operation, on Linux there are two different ways that have to be supported (dbus and xdg), on Mac OS X and Windows there are native APIs.\n\nThis is complicated enough, and would add a compiled module.\n\nOn the other hand, the functionality is embedded somewhere in libchromium. Definitely the better solution.\n"
  },
