    "created_at": "2015-06-12T06:55:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-06-12T07:01:45Z",
    "body": "@baconface Indeed, the Windows solution is not viable. It modifies settings essentially. The proper way is setting thread execution state flag ES_DISPLAY_REQUIRED, which cannot be done without native code.\n\nCurrently it looks like we have viable solutions for OS X and Linux but we don't for world's most popular desktop OS :)\n"
