    "created_at": "2015-06-12T07:26:44Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-06-12T07:26:44Z",
    "body": "This is the power save blocker in Chromium: https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#search/&q=PowerSaveBlockerImpl&sq=package:chromium&type=cs\n\nThis is how it's used -> https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/content/browser/web_contents/web_contents_impl.cc&sq=package:chromium&type=cs&rcl=1434079984&l=3149\n\nAnd here is how it's invoked -> https://code.google.com/p/chromium/codesearch#chromium/src/content/browser/web_contents/web_contents_impl.cc&q=WebContentsImpl::OnMediaPlayingNotification&sq=package:chromium&type=cs&l=3175\n\nThere should be an easy way to integrate that in Electron, and this is easier, more elegant and most importantly - more robust than a node.js module.\n"
  },
